article_title: 'SNL's' Michael Che: Trump's Supporters 'Window-Licking Water Heads,' 'Craziest People in the Country'
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

During the “Weekend Update” on NBC’s “Saturday Night Live” this week, Michael Che blasted Donald Trump supporters, calling them “window lickers” and the “craziest people in the country” while reacting to the GOP front-runner saying his supporters are so loyal they would stick with him even if he stood in the middle of Fifth Avenue and shot somebody.

SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

“Is Trump seriously just now realizing his supporters are a bunch of window-licking water heads?” he asked. “Donald, you are talking to the craziest people in the country. You could literally take off your shoe mid-speech, hold it up to your ear, say you’re getting a call from Batman and they would be quiet until you hung up your shoe.”
